Hopewiser,is,a,UK,based,company,that,specializes,in,address,and,database,management,software,The,Hopewiser,AddressServer,API,allows,users,to,embed,address,lookup,and,verification,functionalities,into,their,own,applications,Users,can,also,use,the,API,to,customize,the,format,in,which,addresses,are,returned,or,retrieve,information,for,a,single,address,field